  <li>September 12: Colors, fonts, images, inspiration and wireframe</li>
  <li>September 19: First draft (mobile) with planned interactions</li>
  <li>September 26: Second draft (mobile) with interactions, first draft (desktop) with planned interactions</li>
  <li>October 3: Mobile prototype, desktop second draft with interactions.</li>
  <li>October 10: Final mobile and desktop prototypes</li>
</ul>
